			<a class="time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3899414%2Fbill-gates-disease-epidemic-ebola-threat-to-humanity-disaster%2F%3Fxid%3Dlinkedinshare&amp;title=Bill+Gates+Thinks+This+Is+the+Deadliest+Threat+to+Humankind" data-event="linkedin" title="Click to post this article to LinkedIn"></a>
			
		</span>
		</div>
	</div>	</header>	<section class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
		
		<figure class="article-hero landscape">
			<img src="https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/bill-gates.jpg?quality=65&amp;strip=color&amp;w=550" itemprop="image" alt="Bill Gates, co-founder of Microsoft and co-chair of the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation, speaks at a breakfast meeting with the theme &quot;Dialogue: Technology Innovation for a Sustainable Future&quot; during the Boao Forum For Asia Annual Conference 2015 in Qionghai city, south Chinas Hainan province, 29 March 2015." data-srcset="https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/bill-gates.jpg?quality=65&amp;strip=color&amp;w=1100 800w, https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/bill-gates.jpg?quality=65&amp;strip=color&amp;w=1100 800w 2x"/>
			<figcaption class="image-caption">
				<span class="credit">Cui haoImaginechina/AP</span>
				<span class="caption">Bill Gates, co-founder of Microsoft and co-chair of the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation, speaks at a breakfast meeting with the theme "Dialogue: Technology Innovation for a Sustainable Future" during the Boao Forum for Asia Annual Conference 2015 in Qionghai city, China's Hainan province, on March 29, 2015 </span>
			</figcaption>
		</figure>
		<h2 class="article-excerpt" itemprop="alternativeHeadline">He says it could kill tens of millions</h2>
		<p>In the next 20 years, is it likely that nuclear war, gigantic earthquakes or asteroids could <a href="http://www.vox.com/2015/5/27/8660249/gates-flu-pandemic" target="_blank">kill</a> 20 million people? Bill Gates doesn&#8217;t think so.</p>
<p>But he did tell <em>Vox</em> that such numbers could be felled by a major outbreak of disease &mdash; something the 59-year-old billionaire believes has a &#8220;well over 50%&#8221; chance of happening in his lifetime.</p>
<p>&#8220;The Ebola epidemic showed me that we&#8217;re not ready for a serious epidemic, an epidemic that would be more infectious and would spread faster than Ebola did. This is the greatest risk of a huge tragedy,&#8221; Gates said, claiming that a serious epidemic could kill more than 10 million people a year.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.vox.com/2015/5/27/8660249/gates-flu-pandemic" target="_blank">Read more at Vox</a></p>
<p class="p1"><div class="video-wrapper brightcove-size-large" data-pos="2" data-continuous="1" data-playlist="0"><object id="bc-video-2951346324001-2" class="BrightcoveExperience"><param name="bgcolor" value="#000000"><param name="width" value="100%"><param name="height" value="100%"><param name="playerID" value="1847503743001"><param name="isVid" value="true"><param name="isUI" value="true"><param name="dynamicStreaming" value="true"><param name="videoSmoothing" value="true"><param name="linkBaseURL" value="http://ti.me/1AzxhYl"><param name="includeAPI" value="true"><param name="templateLoadHandler" value="Time.application.brightcoveFacade._onTemplateLoad"><param name="templateReadyHandler" value="Time.application.brightcoveFacade._onTemplateReady"><param name="wmode" value="opaque"><param name="htmlFallback" value="true"><param name="@videoPlayer" value="2951346324001"></object></div></p>
<p class="p1"><div class="galleryContainer galleryContainer--embedded" data-gallery="3510873" data-size="default"></div></p>

	</section>
