    			<a href="#" class="time-icons time-icons-comment livefyre-commentcount toggle-comments" data-event="comment-lwr" data-lf-site-id="314099" data-lf-article-id="3850998" data-url="http://time.com/3850998/ebola-eye-virus-ian-crozier/" data-title="Doctors Stumped After Ebola Survivor&amp;#8217;s Eye Changed Colors" title="Click to view and post comments">0</a>
