resents the range of Ebola\u2019s emotional impact. In the two women, we see the devastation and loss that the virus causes. In the faces of the men, we see a sense of despondence, disbelief and suspicion that also defines the response. It was a difficult but necessary picture to make.\"","credit":"Pete Muller\u2014Prime for the Washington Post","alt":"Ebola in Sierra Leone for the Washington Post","width":2500,"height":1667,"orientation":"square","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/3507162\/inside-ebola-crisis-moving-photographs\/photo\/ebola-in-sierra-leone-for-the-washington-post-3\/","encoded_url":"http:\/\/time.com\/3507162\/inside-ebola-crisis-moving-photographs\/photo\/ebola-in-sierra-leone-for-the-washington-post-3\/","twitter_via":"TIMEHealth","encoded_title":"Inside+the+Ebola+Crisis%3A+The+Images+that+Moved+them+Most","encoded_shortlink":"http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3507162%2Finside-ebola-crisis-moving-photographs%2Fphoto%2Febola-in-sierra-leone-for-the-washington-post-3%2F","twitter_encoded_shortlink":"http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3507162%2Finside-ebola-crisis-moving-photographs%2Fphoto%2Febola-in-sierra-leone-for-the-washington-post-3%2F","email_title":"Inside%20the%20Ebola%20Crisis%3A%20The%20Images%20that%20Moved%20them%20Most","twitter_text":"See%20inside%20the%20Ebola%20crisis%3A%20the%20images%20that%20moved%20them%20most","fb_text":"See%20inside%20the%20Ebola%20crisis%3A%20the%20images%20that%20moved%20them%20most","email_body":"Inside%20the%20Ebola%20Crisis%3A%20The%20Images%20that%20Moved%20them%20Most%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3507162%2Finside-ebola-crisis-moving-photographs%2Fphoto%2Febola-in-sierra-leone-for-the-washington-post-3%2F","src":{"small":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/10\/peter-muller-ebola1.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=405","small_2x":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/10\/peter-muller-ebola1.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=810","large":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/10\/peter-muller-ebola1.jpg?qualit